<p align="center"><font face="Trebuchet MS" size="1">Redeemed Rake of the 51st
Season</font></p>
<p align="center"><font face="Trebuchet MS" size="1">Legends of Marr</font></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/usophacles.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sophacles</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 33<br> <font color=#333333>(10/9/01 3:46:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Planar Breaks and an Idea</span><hr size=1> Getting your entire raid party down to low health and then zoning in to the planes or any other zone in order to get dumped in the safe spot sounds like an exploit to me...  also, if it doesn't work, you then have a long CR ahead of you.<br>
<br>
As for casting egress in the planes - not a bad idea, and one I plan on suggesting at the end of my next planar experience <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/udoslo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Doslo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#333333>(10/9/01 4:49:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Planar Breaks and an Idea</span><hr size=1> I dont think the low health zoning takes you to a safe spot, it just drops you at the 0,0 coordinate of the zone.  When I hunted in unrest, I remember zoning out with low health, i was dropped in the middle of the lake in DC...not a very safe spot to be (I had some undertow skellies pounding on me when I popped). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/udranthorbloodwraith.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dranthor Bloodwraith</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 48<br> <font color=#333333>(10/12/01 9:27:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Planar Breaks and an Idea</span><hr size=1> Safe spot isnt always safe... Its just the &quot;safe&quot; spot cus thats where you get dumped if you fall thru the world (perhaps your corpse if it 10ks you) <p><a href=http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=49685>Lucsa Kurobuchi</a>, 60th Grandmaster<br>
<b><i>The Dark Breed of Norrath</b></i><br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/umorpainforu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Morpain Foru</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#333333>(10/12/01 5:25:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.home.net/rleophard/morpainpic/Sig.gif height=210 width=100></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Planar Breaks and an Idea</span><hr size=1> As much as I hate to....I have to agree with Lucsa! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  A good example of this is Skyfire. Egress,Levant,Succor, etc all drop you at the &quot;Safe spot&quot;. Well in Skyfire the &quot;safe spot&quot; is just outside the graveyard! NOT a very safe spot! I have personally never tried the spell in any of the planes and really wouldn't suggest it unless you just cleared the ENTIRE plane and want to see where it will put you!<br>
<br>
On the other hand it works GREAT in MOST of the dungeons! MOST of them it will put you at either the zn in or zn out. <p>Morpain Foru<BR>Iksar Warlock of Zebuxoruk<br> Dark Breed of Norrath</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm4.showPrevMessage?topicID=154.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm4.showNextMessage?topicID=154.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic&index=4><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm4.emailToFriend?topicID=154.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm4.threadControl?topicID=154.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm4.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=154.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm4.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=154.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub41.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thecrossroadstavern8833frm42">Board